'''弗莱布许荷兰归正会教堂'''（Flatbush Reformed Protestant Dutch Church）是一个历史悠久的荷兰归正会[[教堂|教堂]]，现在属于[[美国归正会|美国归正会]]，位于美国[[纽约市|纽约市]][[布鲁克林|布鲁克林]]弗莱布许社区的弗莱布许大道890号。教堂建筑群包括教堂、墓地、牧师楼和教会楼。

==历史==
该堂会成立于1654年<ref>Rawson, Elizabeth Reich and Manbeck, John "Flatbush" in {{cite enc-nyc2}}, pp.417-418</ref>。目前的教堂是该地点的第三座教堂建筑。<ref name=aia>{{cite aia5}}, p.711</ref>高2.5层，联邦风格，由托马斯·法尔顿设计建于1793-1798年<ref name=nycland />，有一个石头[[钟楼|钟楼]]。花窗玻璃是蒂芙尼工作室的作品，纪念许多早期定居者的后裔。建筑使用曼哈顿片岩建造，建筑包括[[罗马式建筑|罗马式]]特色如拱形门窗，以及[[托斯卡纳柱式|托斯卡纳柱式]]。<ref name=aia />教堂的钟从[[荷兰|荷兰]]进口，并由约翰·范德比尔特支付。<ref>{{Cite web|title = An historical sketch of the city of Brooklyn, and the surrounding neighborhood : including the village of Williamsburgh, and the towns of Bushwick, Flatbush, Flatlands, New Utrecht, and Gravesend : to which is added an interesting account of the battle of Long Island|url = https://archive.org/stream/historicalsketch03bail#page/32/mode/2up|website = archive.org|accessdate = 2015-12-06}}</ref>

[[美国革命战争|美国革命战争]]期间[[长岛战役|长岛战役]]中死亡的美国士兵尸体埋在教堂建筑物下面。<ref>{{Cite web|title = New York city guide; a comprehensive guide to the five boroughs of the metropolis: Manhattan, Brooklyn, the Bronx, Queens, and Richmond|url = https://archive.org/stream/newyorkcityguide00federich|website = archive.org|accessdate = 2015-12-06}}</ref>

该公墓是弗莱布许大多数早期荷兰家庭的安息之处。最早的可读的坟墓标记可追溯到1754年。1853年的牧师楼是一个2.5层的木框架房子，为介于希腊复兴和意大利风格之间的过渡建筑风格<ref name=nycland />。教会楼是一座2.5层的红砖和[[石灰石|石灰石]]建筑，为殖民地复兴风格，建于1923-24年。<ref name="nrhpinv_ny">{{cite web|url=http://www.oprhp.state.ny.us/hpimaging/hp_view.asp?GroupView=3174|title=National Register of Historic Places Registration:Flatbush Dutch Reformed Church Complex|date=June 1983|accessdate=2011-02-20|author=Larry E. Gobrecht|publisher=[[New_York_State_Office_of_Parks,_Recreation_and_Historic_Preservation|New York State Office of Parks, Recreation and Historic Preservation]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019020345/http://www.oprhp.state.ny.us/hpimaging/hp_view.asp?GroupView=3174|archivedate=2012-10-19}} ''See also:'' {{cite web|url=http://www.oprhp.state.ny.us/hpimaging/hp_view.asp?GroupView=3175|title=Accompanying 10 photos|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121019020403/http://www.oprhp.state.ny.us/hpimaging/hp_view.asp?GroupView=3175|archivedate=2012-10-19}}</ref>

该综合体最初于1966年被指定为[[纽约市地标|纽约市地标]]，其边界在1979年扩大。<ref name=nycland />它于1983年列入[[国家史迹名录|国家史迹名录]]<ref name="nris"/>。

